    dc:description "FIGURE 34. Anthidium (Anthidium) xuezhongi Niu & Zhu, sp. nov.. Male. a: Body in lateral view; b: Head in frontal view; c: Mesosoma in dorsal view; d (d-1): Metasoma in dorsal view, d-1 showing the different pattern of yellow maculations on metasomal terga; e: T7 in dorsal view; f: S5–S6 in ventral view; g: S7 in ventral view; h: S8 in ventral view; i: Genitalia in dorsal view; j: Genitalia in lateral view. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4417151/files/figure.png" ;
